mysql

1.inner join     

conditon = 1=2
two or more  table common only get   =>mongodb project concept 
eg:id another userid same only get 

SELECT users.id, users.name , users.age ,userdetails.id, userdetails.address ,userdetails.process
FROM users users 
INNER JOIN userdetails userdetails
ON users.id=userdetails.id


2.left join

condition =1=>2
left table OR first table (call name)

eg:first table id match to second table all data get If any data null also get  

SELECT users.id,users.name,users.age,userdetails.id 
FROM users users
LEFT JOIN userdetails userdetails 
ON users.id =userdetails.id

3.right join

condition =1<=2
right table OR second table (call name)  

eg:second table id match to first table all data get If any data null also get  

SELECT users.id,users.name,users.age,userdetails.id 
FROM users users
RIGHT JOIN userdetails userdetails 
ON users.id =userdetails.id

